OL,3,CBeluga whales rescued after being
OL,4,Ctrapped in closed down Canadian theme
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FSierra, Bertie Botts, Acadia and
OL,8,FFrankie were among six whales rescued
OL,9,Ffrom the theme park
OL,11,FCredit: CBC
OL,13,FSix Beluga whales have been rescued
OL,14,Ffrom a closed down theme park in
OL,15,FCanada.
OL,17,FThe whales were rescued from
OL,18,FMarineland, a theme park and zoo in
OL,19,FNiagara Falls, which permanently shut
OL,20,Fin 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
