OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784665115
OL,3,CBeluga whales rescued after being
OL,4,Ctrapped in closed down Canadian theme
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FThe marine mammals were pictured being
OL,8,Fairlifted to safety as they prepare to
OL,9,Fembark on their journey to other
OL,10,Faquariums.
OL,12,FThey are the first group of at least
OL,13,F30 whales that will be evacuated.
OL,15,FBeluga whales are one of the smallest
OL,16,Fwhale species. However, they can grow
OL,17,Fup to 15 feet long and weigh up to
OL,18,F1,600kg, meaning they are not the
OL,19,Feasiest of animals to transport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
