PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784665115
OL,3,CBeluga whales rescued after being
OL,4,Ctrapped in closed down Canadian theme
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FCranes, hoists and dozens of staff
OL,8,Ffrom Marineland and US aquariums
OL,9,Fhelped to carefully carry them out of
OL,10,Ftheir pool into individual water
OL,11,Ftanks, which were then loaded onto
OL,12,Ftrucks.
OL,14,FCBC reports that The Department of
OL,15,FFisheries and Oceans Canada (DFO)
OL,16,Fplans to send the whales to either
OL,17,FOceanografic Valencia in Spain or
OL,18,FGeorgia Aquarium, Shedd Aquarium and
OL,19,Ftwo SeaWorld centres in the US.
OL,26,@yD@IqpyD@Qqr
