OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1784665115
OL,3,CBeluga whales rescued after being
OL,4,Ctrapped in closed down Canadian theme
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FMarineland closed to the public in
OL,8,F2024, after CBC reported there had
OL,9,Fbeen multiple whale deaths at the park.
OL,11,FThe animals were threatened with
OL,12,Feuthanasia after the government
OL,13,Fblocked them from being sent to China.
OL,15,FNow the belugas are being saved and
OL,16,Fshipped overseas to different
OL,17,Faquariums.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
