OL,3,CBeluga whales rescued after being
OL,4,Ctrapped in closed down Canadian theme
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FPrior to its closure, Marineland had
OL,13,Ffaced charges of animal cruelty of its
OL,14,Fother animals and in 2021 they were
OL,15,Fcharged for using whales and dolphins
OL,16,Ffor entertainment.
OL,18,FThe park had been running for more
OL,19,Fthan 60 years and housed Keiko the
OL,20,Forca who starred in the hit 90s film
OL,21,FFree Willy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
