OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FHowever there was public backlash over
OL,8,Fthe site's animal welfare after a
OL,9,FToronto Star investigation in 2012
OL,10,Ffound evidence of poor water quality
OL,11,Fand animal neglect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
